  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nOne study evaluated the effects on peatland vegetation of building artificial bird perches. The study was in a tropical peat swamp.\nVegetation cover (1 study): One replicated, paired, controlled study in a peat swamp forest in Indonesia\u00a0found that artificial bird perches had no significant effect on seedling abundance."
